Social icons

Instructions for acquiring icons are in the font awesome files in this folder. 


Icon spacing ideas
Use display:flex; gap:10px; on the parent to create spacing between the icons. 

Displaying social icons on the html page:
<i class="fab fa-facebook"></i>
<i class="fab fa-instagram"></i>
<i class="fab fa-linkedin"></i>

