You can style Font Awesome icons using background-color, color (font color), font-size, padding, margin, text-align, border-radius, box-shadow, and transform (for scaling or rotating) to customize their appearance




Other ways to target groups of social icons:
THE CSS
.social-icons {  
  display: flex;  
  gap: 10px;  
}  

.social-icons i {  
  font-size: 1.5rem;  
  color: #333;  
  transition: color 0.3s ease;  
}  

.social-icons i:hover {  
  color: #007bff; /* Change color on hover */  
}  

THE HTML
<div class="social-icons">  
  <i class="fab fa-facebook"></i>  
  <i class="fab fa-instagram"></i>  
  <i class="fab fa-linkedin"></i>  
</div>  

